Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.78,0:00:15.49,Text-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\b0\bord0\fsp0\fax0.05\1c&H4B4D4D&\move(979.1,1105,880.1,835,0,1695)\frz14.64}你真的和直人分手了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.49,0:00:17.49,Text-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fs120\fsp0\bord0\c&H333033&\fax0.15\frz8.414\pos(991,883.5)}你真的和直人分手了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.49,0:00:21.12,Text-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\b0\fsp0\bord0\fax-0.1\c&H242322&\frz346.3\move(729.22,678.22,729.22,730.23,31,1991)}我们没有分手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:31.17,Text-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord2\c&H414047&\3c&HB9BAD3&\fs40\frz24.87\move(1345,590,1915,590)}给妈妈和小翔\N不嫌弃的话今天也吃饼干吧\N{\fs30}形状虽然不好看但味道还是没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.09,0:19:37.32,Text-CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fsp0\fs40\1c&H21201E&\pos(1510,436)}同样是四年级
